    "TencentChinese": "由<span class=\"name name-tradeable\">气体</span>产物、<span class=\"name name-commodity\">热凝物</span>和<span class=\"name name-commodity\">氮盐</span>制作而成。<br>通过突袭<span class=\"name name-technology\">行星工厂</span>学习相关设计图。",
    "TraditionalChinese": "由<span class=\"name name-tradeable\">氣體</span>產物、<span class=\"name name-commodity\">導熱凝液</span>和<span class=\"name name-commodity\">氮鹽</span>製作而成。<br>襲擊<span class=\"name name-technology\">星球工廠</span>或從<span class=\"name name-special\">太空異常</span>上的<span class=\"name name-stellar\">合成實驗室</span>來了解相關設計圖。"
